{
  "id": "68b95ac52c6d852715da3496",
  "title": "内積で余弦定理を求めるのは逆ではないか",
  "created": 1756977865,
  "updated": 1756979900,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "68b95ac52c6d852715da3496",
      "text": "内積で余弦定理を求めるのは逆ではないか",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756977865,
      "updated": 1756977865
    },
    {
      "id": "68b95ac90000000000c17db6",
      "text": "from [@綾坂こと]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756977866,
      "updated": 1756977875
    },
    {
      "id": "68b95ad40000000000c17db8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756977876,
      "updated": 1756977876
    },
    {
      "id": "68b95ad70000000000c17db9",
      "text": "> [余弦定理]はすぐ上にある[\" ベクトルの内積]が計算面で1番楽だと思います[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756977880,
      "updated": 1756977905
    },
    {
      "id": "68b95ac90000000000c17db7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756977866,
      "updated": 1756977866
    },
    {
      "id": "68b95af20000000000c17dba",
      "text": "余弦定理を思い出すためのツールとしてベクトルの内積は有用[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756977906,
      "updated": 1756977934
    },
    {
      "id": "68b95b0e0000000000c17dbc",
      "text": "\t[$ \\|\\bm b-\\bm a\\|^2=(\\bm b-\\bm a)\\cdot(\\bm b-\\bm a)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756977934,
      "updated": 1756977973
    },
    {
      "id": "68b95b360000000000c17dbd",
      "text": "\t\t[$ =\\|\\bm b\\|^2+\\|\\bm a\\|^2-2\\bm a\\cdot\\bm b]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756977975,
      "updated": 1756978513
    },
    {
      "id": "68b95b5b0000000000c17dbe",
      "text": "\t\t[$ =\\|\\bm b\\|^2+\\|\\bm a\\|^2-2\\|\\bm a\\|\\|\\bm b\\|\\cos\\theta]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756978012,
      "updated": 1756978045
    },
    {
      "id": "68b95af20000000000c17dbb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756977906,
      "updated": 1756977906
    },
    {
      "id": "68b95b880000000000c17dbf",
      "text": "しかし、内積と余弦定理の定義の順序はむしろ逆なのではないかと思う。[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756978057,
      "updated": 1756979900
    },
    {
      "id": "68b95bc00000000000c17dc1",
      "text": "幾何的な考え方での余弦定理はデカルト座標系を経由せずに証明できる。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756978112,
      "updated": 1756978164
    },
    {
      "id": "68b95ea90000000000c17dd1",
      "text": " [https://gyazo.com/89b9a9988cf247e3a378d72ebc89113a]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756978858,
      "updated": 1756979166
    },
    {
      "id": "68b95fe60000000000c17dd3",
      "text": " 左右の直角三角形に三平方の定理を利用する",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756979174,
      "updated": 1756979198
    },
    {
      "id": "68b960220000000000c17dd5",
      "text": " \t[$ \\|\\bm b-\\bm a\\|^2=\\|\\bm b_2\\|^2+\\|\\bm h\\|^2]←右の三角形に三平方の定理",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756979234,
      "updated": 1756979801
    },
    {
      "id": "68b960be0000000000c17dd9",
      "text": " \t\t[$ =(\\|\\bm b\\|-\\|\\bm b_1\\|)^2+\\|\\bm h\\|^2]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756979391,
      "updated": 1756979440
    },
    {
      "id": "68b960f60000000000c17dda",
      "text": " \t\t[$ =\\|\\bm b\\|^2-2\\|\\bm b\\|\\|\\bm b_1\\|+\\|\\bm b_1\\|^2+\\|\\bm h\\|^2]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756979446,
      "updated": 1756979674
    },
    {
      "id": "68b9613e0000000000c17ddb",
      "text": " \t\t[$ =\\|\\bm b\\|^2-2\\|\\bm b\\|\\|\\bm a\\|\\cos\\theta+(\\|\\bm b_1\\|^2+\\|\\bm h\\|^2)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756979518,
      "updated": 1756979749
    },
    {
      "id": "68b961f00000000000c17ddc",
      "text": " \t\t[$ =\\|\\bm b\\|^2-2\\|\\bm b\\|\\|\\bm a\\|\\cos\\theta+\\|\\bm a\\|^2]←左の三角形に三平方の定理",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756979697,
      "updated": 1756979795
    },
    {
      "id": "68b95bf70000000000c17dc2",
      "text": " [$ \\therefore \\|\\bm b-\\bm a\\|^2=\\|\\bm b\\|^2+\\|\\bm a\\|^2-2\\|\\bm a\\|\\|\\bm b\\|\\cos\\theta]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756978168,
      "updated": 1756979860
    },
    {
      "id": "68b95c210000000000c17dc3",
      "text": "\tこの式に対して",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756978210,
      "updated": 1756979844
    },
    {
      "id": "68b95c610000000000c17dc5",
      "text": "\t\t[$ (b-a)^2=b^2+a^2-2ab]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756978273,
      "updated": 1756978290
    },
    {
      "id": "68b95c750000000000c17dc6",
      "text": "\t\tとのアナロジーを見出すのは自然なことだと思う。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756978294,
      "updated": 1756978309
    },
    {
      "id": "68b95c850000000000c17dc7",
      "text": "\t[$ \\bm a\\cdot \\bm b=\\|\\bm a\\|\\bm b\\|\\cos\\theta]なる演算を導入すると、",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756978309,
      "updated": 1756978362
    },
    {
      "id": "68b95cb90000000000c17dc8",
      "text": "\t\t[$ \\bm a\\cdot\\bm a=\\|\\bm a\\|^2\\cos0=\\|\\bm a\\|^2]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756978362,
      "updated": 1756978406
    },
    {
      "id": "68b95ce70000000000c17dc9",
      "text": "\t\tよって、",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756978407,
      "updated": 1756978410
    },
    {
      "id": "68b95cea0000000000c17dca",
      "text": "\t\t[$ \\|\\bm b-\\bm a\\|^2=\\|\\bm b\\|^2+\\|\\bm a\\|^2-2\\bm a\\cdot\\bm b]のように書いたり",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756978410,
      "updated": 1756978564
    },
    {
      "id": "68b95d830000000000c17dcc",
      "text": "\t\t[$ \\|\\bm b-\\bm a\\|^2=(\\bm b-\\bm a)\\cdot(\\bm b-\\bm a)=\\bm b\\cdot\\bm b+\\bm a\\cdot\\bm a-2\\bm a\\cdot\\bm b=\\|\\bm b\\|^2+\\|\\bm a\\|^2-2\\bm a\\cdot\\bm b]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756978564,
      "updated": 1756978668
    },
    {
      "id": "68b95df00000000000c17dcd",
      "text": "\t\t\tのような式変形ができるようになる。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756978673,
      "updated": 1756978680
    },
    {
      "id": "68b95d1e0000000000c17dcb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756978462,
      "updated": 1756978547
    },
    {
      "id": "68b95e420000000000c17dcf",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756978755,
      "updated": 1756978755
    },
    {
      "id": "68b95e450000000000c17dd0",
      "text": "余談",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756978757,
      "updated": 1756978759
    },
    {
      "id": "68b95e290000000000c17dce",
      "text": " 直交座標系でのベクトルを用いた余弦定理の計算があまりにもキレイだから、高校生の時には「絶対にこっちが先やろ」と思っていたが、今は逆。[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756978730,
      "updated": 1756979877
    },
    {
      "id": "68b95c3e0000000000c17dc4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756978239,
      "updated": 1756978239
    }
  ]
}